title: Timi Pari | Lekaki Hey Maya - Kandara | Emperor Kripa Unplugged | Season 3
description:
Since its inception back in 2013 Kripa Drishya Digital has been providing this platform KRIPA UNPLUGGED as a means of showcasing popular Nepali musical talents and their music in a stripped down version bringing to you the raw sounds of acoustic music

This time Kripa Unplugged is back with Season 3 joining hands with our Sponsor Emperor Whiskey

In this episode we have the folk rock band from Pokhara coming together after a long hiatus performing their hit singles Timi Pari released in in 1995 and Lekaki Hey Maya released in 1996. Vocalist Bivek Shrestha flew down from Australia to reunite with his band Kandara just for this special performance for their fans on Kripa Unplugged

title: Lolly Talk 《三分甜》 Official Music Video
description:
#三分甜 #香港女團 #lollytalk #女團 #世一 #女團世一

-親愛的朋友
        如果當天我沒有跟大伙兒在晴空下，唱起那首歌，排過那支舞，我會不會遇見你？

        我只知道，有着各樣性格和故事的我們，在追逐夢想的途上偏偏遇到彼此，真好呢。
         好像每顆音符交織，合奏出動聽的旋律，一起變化，一起經歷更多。
我有時會偷偷想，如果這首由我們友情譜成的樂章有甜味，那應該就是三分甜吧⋯⋯不是多糖，也不是走甜，是健健康康的三分甜～～～

         即使生活總要有七分苦澀無味，尚有三分甜可以送給世一的你，因為那就是我整個宇宙的快樂～
